articles.author: Ivana Kottasová
articles.title: With Kremlin apologist leading the polls, Slovakia vote threatens country’s support for Ukraine - CNN
articles.description: Slovaks have been voting in a knife-edge parliamentary election on Saturday that could radically reshape Slovakia’s approach to Ukraine and create deep rifts within NATO and the European Union.
